description: ASICS has teamed up with Chicago-based boutique Saint Alfred to release a colorway of the Gel Lyte 5 that pays tribute to their hometown, particularly to the Chicago Loop. The Saint Alfred x Gel Lyte 5 'After Dark' features a water-resistant brown nubuck upper with tonal overlays on the side stripes and perforations on the sidewall for breathability. The sneaker also sports matching rip-stop nylon detailing, TexTuff technology in the yellow heel for durability, a GEL-cushioned midsole for comfort, and a Mono Tongue Fit System for an adaptive fit. This shoe is perfect for anyone who loves ASICS sneakers and wants to pay homage to the Windy City.

title: Asics A Bathing Ape x Gel Kayano Trainer 'Brown Camo'
description: Looking for a dope new addition to your sneaker rotation? Check out the Asics A Bathing Ape x Gel Kayano Trainer 'Brown Camo'. This sick collab between Japanese brands ASICS and A Bathing Ape dropped in November 2015 and is already turning heads. The upper is covered in Bape's signature desert camo pattern, with brown suede panels making up the overlays. The Tiger stripes are worked into the lacing system for a nice touch, and a hit of pink marks the outsole's toe and heel. Bape's logo emerges on the heel and camo-print footbed, making this sneaker a must-have for any fan of the brand.

title: Asics Highs and Lows x Gel Lyte 3 'Silverscreen'
description: The Asics Highs and Lows x Gel Lyte 3 'Silverscreen' is a shoe that pays homage to the iconic Perth cinema, The Astor. This runner features a two-tone pastel mint suede and nubuck construction with maroon form stripes on the medial side. Mayan flower detailing inspired by the theatre’s lobby accents the heel and silver deubré, with 3M silver also accenting the toe and lateral form stripes. Other unique details include an embossed HAL logo on the split tongue and a translucent outsole with a print of the theatre’s marble lobby. This shoe is perfect for those who want to add a touch of nostalgia to their style.

title: Asics Invincible x Gel Lyte 3 'Formosa'
description: ASICS' iconic Gel-Lyte 3 silhouette gets a luxe upgrade with this special release from Taiwan-based Invincible. The shoe features a premium hairy suede upper in tonal shades of grey, with pops of navy and red on the heel tab for a touch of contrast. The 'Formosa' moniker carries dual significance: it was Taiwan's name centuries ago and is also part of the scientific name for the crested goshawk, a bird species indigenous to tropical Asia. With its clean lines and sophisticated colorway, the 'Formosa' is a must-have addition to any sneaker collection.

Asics Bait x Gel Lyte 3 'Nightmare'
description: The Asics Bait x Gel Lyte 3 'Nightmare' is a sneaker-like no other. A collaboration between renowned sneaker boutique BAIT and ASICS Tiger, this shoe was made to celebrate the 25th anniversary of the iconic Gel-Lyte 3. The 'Nightmare' iteration of the shoe features a black upper with a combination of smooth and fish scale embossed leathers, while the midsole is contrasted with a speckled effect. The translucent outsole is stamped with BAIT lettering, and the shoe is finished with a leather application on the sockliner and footbed. This sneaker is truly a work of art, and it's perfect for anyone who wants to make a statement.

title: Asics Footpatrol x Gel Lyte 3 'Squad'
description: Asics and Footpatrol join forces once again, this time to celebrate the 25th anniversary of the Gel Lyte 3 silhouette. The limited-edition 'Squad' sneaker is inspired by the iconic gas mask logo of the London retailer, and features a blend of military-inspired earthy hues on its nubuck upper. Perforated detailing and chenille on the collar and split tongue complete the look, while medial mid panels come with olive tiger stripes and gold underlays. Gold Footpatrol branding on the lateral ankle and heel round out the design.

title: Asics Gel Lyte 3 Japanese Denim 'Kimono'
description: The Asics Gel Lyte 3 Japanese Denim 'Kimono' revisits the brand's Japanese roots with a raw Okayama denim textile upper that's complemented with a series of contrasting red hues on the midsole and upper. Yellow accents appear on the edges of the leather formstrips, while the shoe also showcases a floral design on the lining that's reminiscent of traditional Japanese kimonos. This limited-edition shoe is perfect for those who want to add a touch of style to their sneaker collection.

title: Asics Ronnie Fieg x Diamond Supply Co. x Gel Lyte 5 'Tiffany'
description: The ASICS Gel Lyte 5 'Tiffany' is a must-have for any sneakerhead. This limited-edition shoe was a collaboration between Ronnie Fieg and Diamond Supply Co., and features a Diamond Blue perforated pigskin upper. The shoe also has co-branded lace tips and insoles, making it a truly unique piece. The Ronnie Fieg x Diamond x ASICS 'Tiffany' collection was released in June 2015, and also included an ASICS Gel Saga colorway. If you're lucky enough to get your hands on this exclusive shoe, you'll be the envy of all your friends.

title: Asics Ronnie Fieg x Diamond Supply Co. x Gel Saga 'Tiffany'
description: ASICS and Ronnie Fieg have joined forces with Diamond Supply Co. for a special release of the Gel Saga sneaker. This limited-edition sneaker comes in a black and blue colorway, inspired by Diamond Supply's iconic "Tiffany" box. The upper is made of durable micro-perforated leather, with suede details in Tiffany blue on the toe, eyelets, tongue, and formstripes. The leather lining and silver aglets add a luxurious touch, while Ronnie Fieg branding on the heel rounds out the design. This sneaker is perfect for anyone who loves ASICS, Ronnie Fieg, or Diamond Supply Co., and makes a great addition to any collection.

title: Asics Highs and Lows x Gel Lyte 5 'Medic'
description: Looking for a tough and versatile shoe that can take you from the trails to the street? Then check out the Asics Highs and Lows x Gel Lyte 5 'Medic'! This tough and rugged sneaker is inspired by military medics and features perforated suede underlays in olive drab, contrasted by white leather side stripes, red mesh inserts, and black leather paneling at the toe and heel. Special details include tonal splatter detailing on the collar and a glow-in-the-dark midsole. Whether you're hitting the trails or exploring the city, the Asics Highs and Lows x Gel Lyte 5 'Medic' is perfect for any adventure!

title: Asics Size? x Gel Lyte 3 '25th Anniversity Tsavorite'
description: The Size? x Gel Lyte 3 '25th Anniversary Tsavorite' was released in May 2015 as a collaboration between ASICS and the UK retailer. Celebrating the quarter-century mark of the popular silhouette, the design takes inspiration from tsavorite, a traditional 25th-anniversary gemstone. The shoe's all-grey upper combines grey suede with reflective paneling, accented with a bright green finish along the interior for a pop of color. Complete with ASICS'GEL technology in the sole for outstanding cushioning, this shoe is perfect for anyone looking for both style and comfort.

title: Asics Concepts x Gel Lyte 3 'Boston Tea Party'
description: The Concepts x Gel Lyte 3 'Boston Tea Party' is a special colorway released in collaboration with Boston-based brand Concepts. The sneaker pays homage to the Boston Tea Party with its white-based suede upper and red suede paneling on the side panes. Blue suede details on the eyestay, mesh tongue and collar, and metallic patent gold leather on the side stripes complete the look of this eye-catching sneaker.

title: Asics Titolo x Gel Lyte 3 'Papercut'
description: ASICS and Swiss sneaker boutique Titolo teamed up for the Gel Lyte 3 ‘Papercut’ to celebrate the opening of Titolo's new shop in Zurich, Switzerland. This shoe is a tribute to the Swiss craft of scherenschnitt, or paper cutting. Graphic prints on the white leather Tiger stripes, neoprene mesh collar and insole reference the ceiling design of the store, and the shoe comes with a black suede upper with a perforated toe box, split tongue and red accents. celebrating both traditional Swiss craftsmanship and contemporary sneaker culture.

title: Asics Packer Shoes x Gel Lyte 3 'Dirty Buck'
description: The Asics Packer Shoes x Gel Lyte 3 'Dirty Buck' is a special edition shoe released in 2015 to celebrate the 25th anniversary of the Asics Gel Lyte 3. The shoe features a grey-beige suede upper with a salmon-toned sole. Packer's signature typeface is on the heel and tongue label, and there is a co-branded insole. This shoe is perfect for those who want a unique and stylish sneaker that celebrates one of the most popular sneakers of all time.

title: Asics Gel Sight 'World Challenger'
description: ASICS is excited to bring back the GEL-Sight ‘World Challenger’ shoe, originally released for the Barcelona Olympics in 1992. This retro-style was worn by Japan’s competitors with a colorway that represents the Summer Games that year. The shoe features a soft leather construction throughout the upper with an external heel unit that extends onto the midsole to maximize stability. The tongue is branded with a World Challenger logo to round out the Olympic inspiration. The ASICS GEL-Sight ‘World Challenger’ shoe is a great addition to any sneaker collection, and perfect for those who love retro styles with a modern twist.

title: Asics Mita x Gel Lyte 3 '25th Anniversary'
description: To celebrate the 25th anniversary of the Gel-Lyte 3, ASICS collaborated with Mita Sneakers of Japan to release this special edition colorway in January 2015. The upper is a blend of navy blue nubuck on the heel and quarter panel, with royal blue on the side stripes and forefoot. Bright orange accents throughout the upper and tooling add pops of contrasting color. This shoe is perfect for anyone looking for a classic retro runner with a modern twist.

title: Asics LimitEDitions x Gel Lyte 5 'Surredaliste'
description: The Asics LimitEDitions x Gel Lyte 5 'Surredaliste' draws inspiration from surrealist artwork, specifically Salvador Dali's painting The Persistence of Memory. The velvety nubuck upper, insect embellishments on the mono-sockliner, and color scheme are all reference elements from the painting. This shoe is a must-have for any ASICS fan or art lover.

title: Asics Solefly x Gel Lyte 3 'Night Haven'
description: The Asics Solefly x Gel Lyte 3 'Night Haven' is a sneaker that was created through a collaboration between Miami sneaker store SoleFly and Asics. This 2016 shoe is inspired by the popular 1980s TV show, Miami Vice. It features a teal and pink color scheme on the medial side, with a black and white "murdered out" look on the lateral side. The shoe also has reflective detailing on the midsole, laces, and branding, as well as a rope lace design. It is a must-have shoe for any Asics or Solefly fan, and is sure to turn heads when you step out in it.

title: Asics Commonwealth Gel Lyte 5 'Gemini'
description: The Asics Commonwealth Gel Lyte 5 'Gemini' is a playful take on the concept of twins. The left and right shoes feature mismatched leather and suede compositions, both finished in matching blue colorways. Shared details include a neoprene bootie construction, contrasting Off-White Gel-cushioned midsoles, and reflective detailing on the laces. This unique sneaker is sure to turn heads wherever you go.

title: Asics Ronnie Fieg x Gel Lyte 5 'Sage'
description: The Ronnie Fieg x Gel Lyte 5 'Sage' is a must-have for any sneakerhead. This premium sneaker features a sage pigskin leather vamp with sea-green overlays, a white leather heel wrap, and 'scratched' detailing on the heel counter. It also comes with an open mesh sockliner and a subtle safari print on the Aqua Blue formstripes and heel tabs. This sneaker dropped in August 2014 alongside the Ronnie Fieg x Asics Gel Lyte 5 'Rose Gold' colorway, and is sure to turn heads wherever you go.

title: Asics Ronnie Fieg x Gel Lyte 5 'Rose Gold'
description: The Ronnie Fieg x Gel Lyte 5 'Rose Gold' is a beautiful colorway that was inspired by the limited-edition GT 2 'Rose Gold' from 2012. It features rose gold pigskin suede on the upper with tonal pink details, white 3M formstripes, and blue 3M formstripes. The blue liner and heel counter with scratched-detailing complete the look of this sneaker that dropped in August 2014.

title: Asics Ubiq x GT Cool 'Nightshade'
description: Asics Ubiq x GT Cool 'Nightshade' is a special edition sneaker created in collaboration with Philadelphia-based retailer UBIQ. The design takes inspiration from the hues of dusk and features a reflective material on the logo, heel-tab, and underlay that’s revealed through perforations in the earthy olive suede upper. The gel-cushioned runner also comes with neon green-backed leather form stripes, two-tone rope laces, and a neon green accent wrapping around the heel. This limited-edition sneaker is perfect for those who love stylish, comfortable footwear that makes a statement.

title: Asics Ronnie Fieg x GT 2 'Brazil'
description: The Ronnie Fieg x ASICS GT 2 'Brazil' is a special edition shoe created to celebrate the 2014 World Cup. This shoe features a royal blue suede upper with metallic gold stripes and yellow accents. The laces are patterned, and the overall design is luxurious and eye-catching. This shoe is perfect for any World Cup fan or shoe collector.

title: Asics Ubiq x Gel Lyte 5 'Midnight Bloom'
description: The Ubiq x Gel Lyte 5 'Midnight Bloom' is a limited-edition shoe from ASICS and the American brand UBIQ is perfect for stylish individuals who want to stand out from the crowd. The white mesh upper is accented with leather and suede overlays in pink, light grey, and black, for a feminine yet edgy look. Nubuck details in navy pay tribute to the midnight sky, while the Gel Lyte midsole provides responsive cushioning all day long.

title: Asics Ronnie Fieg x Gel Lyte 5 'Cove'
description: The ASICS Ronnie Fieg x Gel Lyte 5 'Cove' is a must-have sneaker for any fashion-savvy individual. This limited-edition sneaker features pigskin nubuck upper in a beautiful aqua colorway, perforated underlays, and tonal branding throughout. Whether you're pairing them with your favorite denim or Athleisure looks, these sneakers are sure to make a statement.

title: Asics Ronnie Fieg x Gel Lyte 5 'Mint Leaf'
description: The Ronnie Fieg x ASICS Gel Lyte 5 'Mint Leaf' is a must-have for any sneaker collection. This limited-edition sneaker features soft pigskin nubuck upper with ventilated mesh underlays in a signature mint green hue. Tonal branding on the midsole, midfoot, and tongue completes the iconic look. This sneaker was released in 2013 and quickly became a coveted item for sneakerheads and fashionistas alike. If you're lucky enough to get your hands on a pair, make sure to take good care of them because they're sure to go up in value!

title: Asics Bait x Gel Lyte 3 'Guardian'
description: The Asics Bait x Gel Lyte 3 'Guardian' is a tough and rugged sneaker that is designed to withstand any condition. The upper is made with a combination of nailhead suede and metal wire mesh, finished in a custom jacquard camouflage print. Special details include waxed rope laces, a speckled midsole, and honeycomb 3M reflective detailing on the quarter panel, visible underneath the signature black leather tiger stripes. This sneaker is perfect for anyone who wants a shoe that can handle any terrain and any condition.

title: Asics Ronnie Fieg x Gel Lyte 5 'Volcano'
description: The 'Volcano' edition of the ASICS Gel-Lyte 5, created by Ronnie Fieg in 2013, is a fiery take on the classic 1993 silhouette. The sneaker features a bootie construction, gel-cushioned sole, and a combination of nubuck, mesh, pigskin and neoprene material on the upper for a unique look and feel. The bold burgundy, red, and pink colorway is perfect for making a statement, whether you're hitting the streets or the gym.

title: Asics Ronnie Fieg x Gel Lyte 3 'Flamingo'
description: The Ronnie Fieg x Gel Lyte 3 'Flamingo' is a shoe like no other. Inspired by the wild flamingos that transition from grey to pink, this show features an Ash Grey nubuck upper with tonal mesh on the toe box and quarter panel. Salmon underlays emerge on the leather Tiger stripes and the toe box, while a blue neoprene lining and outsole complete the look. Stitched insole boasts memory foam cushioning for added comfort. This shoe is truly one of a kind - you won't find anything else like it on the market!

title: Asics Saint Alfred x Gel Lyte 3 'Lake Shore'
description: The Saint Alfred x ASICS Gel Lyte 3 'Lake Shore' is a special edition shoe that was created in collaboration with Chicago-based boutique St. Alfred. This shoe is inspired by the water and beaches of the Windy City, and features an olive suede upper with perforated detailing on the toe and quarter panel. The shoe also has the traditional split tongue design, and is equipped with a Gel-cushioned Birch midsole for superior comfort. The gum rubber outsole provides excellent traction and durability.

The Saint Alfred x Gel Lyte 5 'After Dark' features a water-resistant brown nubuck upper with tonal overlays on the side stripes and perforations on the sidewall for breathability. The sneaker also sports matching rip-stop nylon detailing, TexTuff technology in the yellow heel for durability, a GEL-cushioned midsole for comfort, and a Mono Tongue Fit System for an adaptive fit. This shoe is perfect for anyone who loves ASICS sneakers and wants to pay homage to the Windy City.

The upper is covered in Bape's signature desert camo pattern, with brown suede panels making up the overlays. The Tiger stripes are worked into the lacing system for a nice touch, and a hit of pink marks the outsole's toe and heel. Bape's logo emerges on the heel and camo-print footbed, making this sneaker a must-have for any fan of the brand.

title: Asics Highs and Lows x Gel Lyte 3 'Silverscreen'
description: The Asics Highs and Lows x Gel Lyte 3 'Silverscreen' is a shoe that pays homage to the iconic Perth cinema, The Astor. This runner features a two-tone pastel mint suede and nubuck construction with maroon form stripes on the medial side. Mayan flower detailing inspired by the theatre’s lobby accents the heel and silver deubré, with 3M silver also accenting the toe and lateral form stripes. Other unique details include an embossed HAL logo on the split tongue and a translucent outsole with a print of the theatre’s marble lobby. This shoe is perfect for those who want to add a touch of nostalgia to their style.

The 'Formosa' moniker carries dual significance: it was Taiwan's name centuries ago and is also part of the scientific name for the crested goshawk, a bird species indigenous to tropical Asia. With its clean lines and sophisticated colorway, the 'Formosa' is a must-have addition to any sneaker collection.

title: Asics Gel Lyte 3 Japanese Denim 'Kimono'

description: The Concepts x Gel Lyte 3 'Boston Tea Party' is a special colorway released in collaboration with Boston-based brand Concepts. description: ASICS and Swiss sneaker boutique Titolo teamed up for the Gel Lyte 3 ‘Papercut’ to celebrate the opening of Titolo's new shop in Zurich, Switzerland. This shoe is a tribute to the Swiss craft of scherenschnitt, or paper cutting. Graphic prints on the white leather Tiger stripes, neoprene mesh collar and insole reference the ceiling design of the store, and the shoe comes with a black suede upper with a perforated toe box, split tongue and red accents. celebrating both traditional Swiss craftsmanship and contemporary sneaker culture.

description: The Asics Packer Shoes x Gel Lyte 3 'Dirty Buck' is a special edition shoe released in 2015 to celebrate the 25th anniversary of the Asics Gel Lyte 3. This shoe is perfect for those who want a unique and stylish sneaker that celebrates one of the most popular sneakers of all time.

title: Asics Gel Sight 'World Challenger'
description: ASICS is excited to bring back the GEL-Sight ‘World Challenger’ shoe, originally released for the Barcelona Olympics in 1992. This retro-style was worn by Japan’s competitors with a colorway that represents the Summer Games that year. The shoe features a soft leather construction throughout the upper with an external heel unit that extends onto the midsole to maximize stability. The tongue is branded with a World Challenger logo to round out the Olympic inspiration. The ASICS GEL-Sight ‘World Challenger’ shoe is a great addition to any sneaker collection, and perfect for those who love retro styles with a modern twist.

Bright orange accents throughout the upper and tooling add pops of contrasting color. This shoe is perfect for anyone looking for a classic retro runner with a modern twist.

description: The Asics LimitEDitions x Gel Lyte 5 'Surredaliste' draws inspiration from surrealist artwork, specifically Salvador Dali's painting The Persistence of Memory. The velvety nubuck upper, insect embellishments on the mono-sockliner, and color scheme are all reference elements from the painting. This shoe is a must-have for any ASICS fan or art lover.

description: The Asics Solefly x Gel Lyte 3 'Night Haven' is a sneaker that was created through a collaboration between Miami sneaker store SoleFly and Asics. This 2016 shoe is inspired by the popular 1980s TV show, Miami Vice. It features a teal and pink color scheme on the medial side, with a black and white "murdered out" look on the lateral side. The shoe also has reflective detailing on the midsole, laces, and branding, as well as a rope lace design. It is a must-have shoe for any Asics or Solefly fan, and is sure to turn heads when you step out in it.

The gel-cushioned runner also comes with neon green-backed leather form stripes, two-tone rope laces, and a neon green accent wrapping around the heel. description: The Ronnie Fieg x ASICS Gel Lyte 5 'Mint Leaf' is a must-have for any sneaker collection. This limited-edition sneaker features soft pigskin nubuck upper with ventilated mesh underlays in a signature mint green hue. Tonal branding on the midsole, midfoot, and tongue completes the iconic look. This sneaker was released in 2013 and quickly became a coveted item for sneakerheads and fashionistas alike. If you're lucky enough to get your hands on a pair, make sure to take good care of them because they're sure to go up in value!

title: Asics Bait x Gel Lyte 3 'Guardian'
description: The Asics Bait x Gel Lyte 3 'Guardian' is a tough and rugged sneaker that is designed to withstand any condition. The upper is made with a combination of nailhead suede and metal wire mesh, finished in a custom jacquard camouflage print. Special details include waxed rope laces, a speckled midsole, and honeycomb 3M reflective detailing on the quarter panel, visible underneath the signature black leather tiger stripes. This sneaker is perfect for anyone who wants a shoe that can handle any terrain and any condition.

title: Asics Ronnie Fieg x Gel Lyte 5 'Volcano'
description: The 'Volcano' edition of the ASICS Gel-Lyte 5, created by Ronnie Fieg in 2013, is a fiery take on the classic 1993 silhouette. The sneaker features a bootie construction, gel-cushioned sole, and a combination of nubuck, mesh, pigskin and neoprene material on the upper for a unique look and feel. The bold burgundy, red, and pink colorway is perfect for making a statement, whether you're hitting the streets or the gym.

title: Asics Ronnie Fieg x Gel Lyte 3 'Flamingo'
description: The Ronnie Fieg x Gel Lyte 3 'Flamingo' is a shoe like no other. Inspired by the wild flamingos that transition from grey to pink, this show features an Ash Grey nubuck upper with tonal mesh on the toe box and quarter panel. Salmon underlays emerge on the leather Tiger stripes and the toe box, while a blue neoprene lining and outsole complete the look. Stitched insole boasts memory foam cushioning for added comfort. This shoe is truly one of a kind - you won't find anything else like it on the market!

title: Asics Saint Alfred x Gel Lyte 3 'Lake Shore'
description: The Saint Alfred x ASICS Gel Lyte 3 'Lake Shore' is a special edition shoe that was created in collaboration with Chicago-based boutique St. Alfred. This shoe is inspired by the water and beaches of the Windy City, and features an olive suede upper with perforated detailing on the toe and quarter panel. The shoe also has the traditional split tongue design, and is equipped with a Gel-cushioned Birch midsole for superior comfort. The gum rubber outsole provides excellent traction and durability.
